OL,3,CKemi Badenoch tells firms to quit
OL,4,Cpolitical activism and focus on
OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch has
OL,8,Ftold firms to focus on delivering for
OL,9,Fcustomers rather than "activism or
OL,10,Fpolitical causes".
OL,12,FShe said there was a "creeping ` and
OL,13,Fcounter-productive ` politicisation"
OL,14,Fof business. Ms Badenoch said some
OL,15,Ffirms' well-meaning "equality,
OL,16,Fdiversity and inclusion" initiatives
OL,17,F"divide, rather than unify".
