OL,7,FThe business secretary was speaking in
OL,8,Fsupport of a research programme by the
OL,9,FPolicy Exchange think tank on the
OL,10,Fissue.
OL,12,FA Deltapoll survey for the think tank
OL,13,Ffound 50% of people thought businesses
OL,14,Fhad become "too concerned with taking
OL,15,Fpolitical positions on contested
OL,16,Fissues", with 14% disagreeing ` the
OL,17,Fremainder either did not agree or
OL,18,Fdisagree, or did not know.
