OL,7,FThe polling indicated that 75% of
OL,8,Fpeople believe that companies should
OL,9,Fhire on merit, regardless of race or
OL,10,Fgender, instead of seeking to create a
OL,11,Fdiverse team.
OL,13,FThe centre-right think tank's project
OL,14,Fwill "methodically document and
OL,15,Faddress the role and influence of
OL,16,Fsocial and ideological considerations
OL,17,Fon contemporary business",
OL,18,Fparticularly "at the expense of
OL,19,Fshareholder and wider society
OL,20,Finterests".
