OL,7,FPolicy Exchange highlighted examples
OL,8,Fsuch as the debanking row, ice cream
OL,9,Fbrand Ben & Jerry's criticism of the
OL,10,Fgovernment over asylum policies and
OL,11,Fcoffee chain Costa's mural showing a
OL,12,Ftransgender person with mastectomy
OL,13,Fscars sipping a drink on one of its
OL,14,Fexpress vans.
OL,16,FMs Badenoch said: "Policy Exchange's
OL,17,Ffindings confirm what I know to be
OL,18,Ftrue from talking to people who run
OL,19,Fbusinesses, work in them, and buy from
OL,20,Fthem.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
