OL,3,CKemi Badenoch tells firms to quit
OL,4,Cpolitical activism and focus on
OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,F"The public want the focus of business
OL,8,Fto be on delivering great products and
OL,9,Fservices, not activism or political
OL,10,Fcauses ` which repel as many people as
OL,11,Fthey attract.
OL,13,F"Overwhelmingly, people want companies
OL,14,Fto recruit on merit, selecting the
OL,15,Fbest person for the job without regard
OL,16,Fto race or gender, rather than social
OL,17,Fengineering to create 'diverse teams'."
