OL,7,FEarlier this year, an independent
OL,8,Fpanel appointed by Ms Badenoch found
OL,9,Fbusinesses are implementing diversity
OL,10,Fand inclusion initiatives without an
OL,11,Fevidence base.
OL,13,FMs Badenoch said: "As the recent
OL,14,FInclusion at Work Panel showed, many
OL,15,Fwell-meaning 'equality, diversity and
OL,16,Finclusion' initiatives divide rather
OL,17,Fthan unify, and undermine
OL,18,Forganisational goals.
OL,26,@uD@SOU
