OL,3,CKemi Badenoch tells firms to quit
OL,4,Cpolitical activism and focus on
OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,F"They are based on speculative and
OL,8,Fcontested theories with limited
OL,9,Fevidence of impact. Policy Exchange's
OL,10,Fprogramme is a timely and welcome
OL,11,Fcontribution to document the creeping
OL,12,F` and counter-productive `
OL,13,Fpoliticisation of our business
OL,14,Fenvironment.
OL,16,F"I am committed to working with
OL,17,Fbusinesses on effective ways to foster
OL,18,Feconomic growth, and also on this
OL,19,Fgovernment's Inclusive Britain goals `
OL,20,Fsmarter ways to achieve true equality
OL,21,Fof opportunity."
