OL,7,FPolicy Exchange senior research fellow
OL,8,FLara Brown said: "Customers do not
OL,9,Fbelieve that businesses need to
OL,10,Fdemonstrate commitment to progressive
OL,11,Fprinciples and do not make spending
OL,12,Fdecisions based on the political
OL,13,Fstatements of retailers.
OL,15,F"Employees are also negatively
OL,16,Faffected by the politicisation of
OL,17,Fbusiness, with many sceptical about
OL,18,Fworkplace schemes tailored towards
OL,19,Fequality, diversity and inclusion."
